  "history": "Rachel has a pattern of recurring relationship problems with her husband Ivan, which may contribute to ongoing emotional distress. She is under significant work-related stress, recently intensified by being laid off and actively searching for new employment. Her sister Emma often takes a caring, supportive role, which may provide comfort but also foster dependency. Rachel's father had a successful career and strong work ethic, shaping Rachel's high expectations for herself and her sense of self-worth. These influences appear to contribute to her self-critical thinking and vulnerability to feelings of inadequacy, especially in the face of setbacks like job rejection.",
